WEBVTT

00:04.518 --> 00:06.393
- Caroline is...
- Possessed.

00:06.394 --> 00:08.173
Her possession is not a delusion.

00:08.173 --> 00:10.909
That's not holy water. I switched it.

00:10.910 --> 00:12.535
That was not your place, Kristen.

00:12.536 --> 00:14.861
If you want to experiment,
you talk to me.

00:14.862 --> 00:16.227
You don't just do it.

00:16.228 --> 00:17.386
I'm Sheryl.

00:17.387 --> 00:19.813
Leland. I'm gonna leave now,

00:19.814 --> 00:21.715
but I'll wait outside around the corner.

00:23.627 --> 00:25.061
Ketamine and caps.

00:26.830 --> 00:29.131
Where are you, God?

