Okay, what's going on?

00:44.615 --> 00:46.983
What do you mean?

00:46.984 --> 00:49.552
You two, the silence.

00:49.553 --> 00:51.654
We have nothing to say.

00:55.759 --> 00:57.693
A prophet?

00:57.694 --> 00:58.728
Yep.

00:58.729 --> 01:00.563
Have you ever done one of those?

01:00.564 --> 01:01.731
Nope.

01:03.934 --> 01:08.804
So, we find out if she's
real or not, is that it?

01:08.805 --> 01:10.306
Yep.

01:13.210 --> 01:14.377
Well...

01:14.378 --> 01:17.013
you two are a barrel
of fun this morning.

01:33.497 --> 01:34.521
Hey.

01:34.522 --> 01:38.067
_

01:38.068 --> 01:39.969
- You from the Church?
- _

01:39.970 --> 01:41.771
- Yes.
- Please, come in.

01:48.512 --> 01:49.712
It's playtime.

01:49.713 --> 01:51.881
It'll be like this for
the next ten minutes.

01:58.422 --> 02:00.623
Your home is in danger.

02:00.624 --> 02:02.625
Leave before it falls into darkness.

02:05.729 --> 02:07.930
What does that mean?

02:11.802 --> 02:12.835
Grace.

02:15.839 --> 02:18.207
Hello. I'm Grace.

02:18.208 --> 02:19.909
Would you like to sit?

02:19.910 --> 02:21.010
- Sure.
- Thank you.

02:21.011 --> 02:22.878
I'm-I'm David, and this is, uh,

02:22.879 --> 02:24.046
Kristen and Ben.

02:24.047 --> 02:25.548
- Hello.
- Nice to meet you.

02:25.549 --> 02:26.949
Would you like me to call nap time?

02:26.950 --> 02:28.617
Uh, no, it's fine.

02:29.301 --> 02:30.720
So...

02:30.721 --> 02:33.089
you want to know if God speaks to me?

02:34.591 --> 02:35.858
Yes.

02:35.859 --> 02:37.159
He does.

02:39.196 --> 02:41.197
How does God speak to you?

02:42.232 --> 02:44.467
Very slowly.

02:45.535 --> 02:46.869
You can hear him?

02:46.870 --> 02:48.237
Yes.

02:48.238 --> 02:49.572
And what does he sound like?

02:49.573 --> 02:51.407
A whisper, very quiet.

02:51.408 --> 02:52.641
Do you see him?

02:52.642 --> 02:54.477
No.

02:55.512 --> 02:57.279
Can you hear him now?

02:58.982 --> 03:00.583
No.

03:00.584 --> 03:02.084
Why is that?

03:02.085 --> 03:03.919
He has nothing to say.

03:07.691 --> 03:10.326
Do you wait for him to
have something to say?

03:10.327 --> 03:11.961
Sometimes.

03:11.962 --> 03:14.730
And sometimes I ask him a question.

03:16.299 --> 03:19.001
- Can you ask him a question now?
- Yes.

03:23.607 --> 03:25.741
Did you have a question?

03:27.244 --> 03:29.311
Was Jeffrey Epstein a suicide?

03:29.312 --> 03:30.713
- Ben.
- What?

03:30.714 --> 03:32.515
No.

03:34.084 --> 03:36.318
How was he killed?

03:37.554 --> 03:39.722
With a pillow.

03:39.723 --> 03:41.724
Why was he killed?

03:41.725 --> 03:44.894
Because he could hurt
several powerful men.

03:46.263 --> 03:49.131
It seems like an odd way
to deal out prophecies,

03:49.132 --> 03:51.167
to just give them to whoever asks.

03:52.202 --> 03:54.437
As opposed to... ?

03:56.706 --> 03:58.374
So you can...

03:58.375 --> 04:00.576
tell me what God wants of me?

04:00.577 --> 04:02.778
Yes.

04:02.779 --> 04:04.980
What does God want of me?

04:28.505 --> 04:30.306
You're in danger.

04:30.307 --> 04:33.242
In what way?

04:33.243 --> 04:36.479
They know about your visions,
and they want to stop you.

04:39.416 --> 04:42.751
You need to avoid the color
red for the next seven days.

04:44.788 --> 04:48.357
It sounds more like a...
a fortune cookie than God.

04:48.358 --> 04:51.327
Sometimes God sounds
like a fortune cookie.

04:51.328 --> 04:53.629
Why'd you blow that up?

04:53.630 --> 04:57.026
Sometimes when God's
voice gets too quiet,

04:57.027 --> 04:59.034
it helps me hear him.

05:12.115 --> 05:14.049
So?

05:15.085 --> 05:17.553
She certainly appears sincere.

05:17.554 --> 05:19.555
Is that enough?

05:19.556 --> 05:20.856
No.

05:20.857 --> 05:23.959
Does she claim to prophesy
in the name of Jesus?

05:23.960 --> 05:25.094
Yes.

05:25.095 --> 05:26.695
And?

05:26.696 --> 05:28.964
Well, I can claim to
prophesy in the name of Jesus.

05:28.965 --> 05:30.466
The question is: Am I right?

05:30.467 --> 05:31.867
Is she right?

05:31.868 --> 05:33.435
First, may I ask,

05:33.436 --> 05:35.437
why are we being handed this?

05:35.438 --> 05:37.206
Because it's your job.

05:37.207 --> 05:38.641
No.

05:38.642 --> 05:41.143
Millions of people claim
to speak in God's name.

05:41.144 --> 05:43.646
If you gave us every one,
we'd be chasing for decades.

05:43.647 --> 05:44.780
Why this one?

05:46.209 --> 05:48.034
We want to know if she's right.

05:48.035 --> 05:50.019
- Has she been right before?
- Yes.

05:50.020 --> 05:52.888
- With what?
- I can't answer that.

05:52.889 --> 05:55.991
Check her prophecies. Then we'll talk.

05:59.663 --> 06:02.097
- What was that about?
- Yeah.

06:02.098 --> 06:03.499
No idea.

06:03.500 --> 06:06.335
But there was a scribe there
taking down her prophecies.

06:06.336 --> 06:08.637
- Mm-hmm.
- Let's check her prophecies with the facts.

06:08.638 --> 06:10.239
Yep. Yep.

06:10.240 --> 06:12.508
Hey, Kristen, you got a second?

06:15.045 --> 06:16.412
We disagree.

06:16.413 --> 06:18.247
About this prophecy?

06:18.248 --> 06:21.350
About last night. The exorcism.

06:21.351 --> 06:23.619
But it should be a strength,
not a weakness.

06:23.620 --> 06:25.293
Oh, I thought it was.

06:25.294 --> 06:27.890
It was until you didn't trust
me and poured out the holy water.

06:27.891 --> 06:29.091
It was the only way to tell.

06:29.092 --> 06:30.960
No, it wasn't, but even if it was,

06:30.961 --> 06:32.361
trust me enough to tell me.

06:32.362 --> 06:34.897
And if I had told you, would
you have told the exorcist?

06:34.898 --> 06:36.765
- Yes.
- Which would negate the whole experiment.

06:36.766 --> 06:38.534
It wasn't the place for an experiment.

06:38.535 --> 06:39.926
Oh, every place is the
place for an experiment.

06:39.927 --> 06:41.852
It's the only way not to
let opinion impact results.

06:41.853 --> 06:43.606
Then trust me enough
to argue that with me,

06:43.607 --> 06:45.674
and we'll discuss.

06:45.675 --> 06:47.910
Do you have any idea how weird it is

06:47.911 --> 06:49.478
for me to be involved in this?

06:49.479 --> 06:51.614
I mean, I go to Whole
Foods during the day,

06:51.615 --> 06:53.115
and at night I say things like,

06:53.116 --> 06:54.717
"Would you have told the exorcist?"

06:54.718 --> 06:58.053
It's like I've taken a left
turn into the Middle Ages.

07:00.890 --> 07:02.625
Okay.

07:02.626 --> 07:05.304
See you tomorrow.

07:05.305 --> 07:07.697
No, it wasn't, but even if it was,

07:07.698 --> 07:09.232
trust me enough to tell me.

07:09.233 --> 07:11.868
And if I had told you, would
you have told the exorcist?

07:11.869 --> 07:13.694
- Yes.
- Which would negate the whole experiment.

07:13.695 --> 07:15.086
It wasn't the place for an experiment.

07:15.087 --> 07:17.946
Oh, every place is the
place for an experiment.

07:25.487 --> 07:27.779
- Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.
- What?

07:29.806 --> 07:31.197
This is wrong.

07:31.198 --> 07:32.999
No, it's not.

07:41.531 --> 07:43.666
No, it's not right.

07:43.667 --> 07:45.067
Why not?

07:45.068 --> 07:47.470
Come on, baby, kiss me again.

07:47.471 --> 07:49.739
I want you so bad.

07:57.724 --> 07:59.748
_

08:01.141 --> 08:02.332
Who are you calling?

08:02.333 --> 08:03.590
Kristen.

08:03.591 --> 08:06.384
I had a scare with my
granddaughters the other night.

08:06.385 --> 08:09.492
Oh. Let's go. This is my song.

08:09.493 --> 08:11.327
It's always your song.

08:12.496 --> 08:14.597
So, what am I typing in?

08:14.598 --> 08:16.399
"Local sinkhole".

08:16.400 --> 08:18.901
Local sinkhole.

08:21.872 --> 08:24.507
A 30-foot sinkhole
opened in Queens overnight.

08:24.508 --> 08:27.043
As the grounds settled
from a recent rainstorm,

08:27.044 --> 08:29.136
the dirt lot disappeared
into the ground.

08:29.137 --> 08:30.567
But many lives were spared

08:30.568 --> 08:31.714
- because of one woman.
- I don't understand.

08:31.715 --> 08:33.515
- I was warned.
- What does this... ?

08:33.517 --> 08:34.984
That's why I moved out.

08:34.985 --> 08:37.053
And I warned my neighbor, too.

08:37.054 --> 08:40.423
Wait, is that her, the-the
lady from the day care?

08:40.424 --> 08:42.525
- Yes.
- What was the prophecy?

08:42.525 --> 08:45.061
"Leave your home.

08:45.062 --> 08:47.897
It's in danger of falling
into the darkness".

08:49.166 --> 08:51.167
I need to talk to her again.

08:51.168 --> 08:52.902
Yes.

08:52.903 --> 08:55.438
We both do.

